citations:
    citation-affc-samwell-iii:
        source: source-affc
        properties:
            locator: "Samwell III"
            text_from_source: "He ran. It was a long way over slick cobbles."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Sam in Braavos confronts Dareon the singer at the Happy Port, who has deserted the Night's Watch. Sam beats Dareon in a brawl and is thrown in a canal. He is rescued by Xhondo, a Summer Islander who serves on the Cinnamon Wind, who tells Sam he has seen dragons in Qarth. Maester Aemon is very ill. The chapter establishes that Arya later killed Dareon."
